{"tid":2497204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李卓人憂遭加料控違國安法","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T11:05:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d58a093b4d961f9a5ad8cd5635e7c0a1f6f569fa","tid":2497204,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/KPWBPLFEIJCV7BCGAXLTV3NZP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FKPWBPLFEIJCV7BCGAXLTV3NZP4%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=6a489464\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FKPWBPLFEIJCV7BCGAXLTV3NZP4%2F&h=75920324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/KPWBPLFEIJCV7BCGAXLTV3NZP4/</a><br />\n<br />\n李卓人憂遭加料控違國安法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2t9gGYNx2DRaCaoxY4AszCalkKI=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FHMXWJYPSZFVXBY3KA4ZUA4SNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2t9gGYNx2DRaCaoxY4AszCalkKI%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFHMXWJYPSZFVXBY3KA4ZUA4SNA.jpg&h=76f7daff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李卓人盼港人今年六四可在不同地方燃點燭光。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】支聯會主席李卓人因前年參與8.18及8.31兩場未經批准集會，被判囚14個月，他入獄前兩日接受多年戰友、職工盟總幹事蒙兆達訪問時形容，認為入獄與因初選被控串謀顛覆國家政權罪被扣押的47名人比較「好渺小」，而他最擔心會否遭當局「加料」告他干犯國安法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盼港人六四夜續點燭光<br />\n<br />\n李卓人在D100節目「真工道」訪問中分享如何度過入獄前日子，除忙於搬屋及約見朋友，亦準備好入獄期間希望閱讀的書，相信入獄是「重新整理自己、思考嘅時間」。<br />\n<br />\n李認為自己入獄，相對47名人因初選被扣押的冤案「其實係好渺小」，反擔心自己會否突遭當局誣告干犯國安法：「我過去做嘅嘢全部公開，要『加料』唔係難，國安法任佢哋點詮釋，紅線任佢哋講講，係隨時可以『加料』。」<br />\n<br />\n64歲的李卓人指港府對人民打壓比港英時代更赤裸，隨着近年未再出任立會議員，加上社會思潮改變及國安法出台，「真係幾迷失」，「呢段時間真係低潮，我個樣樂觀，但真係唔知呢個黑暗時間要幾耐，幾時過去無人知」<br />\n<br />\n由於今年六四身在獄中，六四集會重擔會由其他人肩負，李相信難度更大，但支聯會成員將堅持進入維園點起燭光，巿民今年即使不進入維園，亦可在不同地方燃點燭光，「人心不死已經足夠」，又寄語港人「燈在，人在」，只要堅守崗位，包括在專業上頂住不合理要求，非政府組織和工會繼續維護行業權益，向政府提出訴求，「大家先會有希望。」"},{"pid":"c7a7a938523f0e89bc1a6a52d1c6beb596e6b1ed","tid":2497204,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f536b58dca1c307220061b9a4b807e093de4a086","tid":2497204,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06e9952fd185873e44181a6b0fef8eeccd2b8bd","tid":2497204,"uid":85127,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"其實中國發生既事，關香港乜事？<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你去悼念緬甸，非洲d野？<br />\n<br />\n你全家都是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCPC就係要你呢d身份認同 <br />\n<br />\n習慣做下港豬儲錢移民好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2c590e53ad6c0f6dbcbf18ff4c245183bc4696","tid":2497204,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"依家真係可以殉道"},{"pid":"152f1b669cd554b1dcda054357f020d03c1aae18","tid":2497204,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"老柒講職工盟其實都好黑化下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe205e4f62703144c9fa0dca6ebf2a79f53742a","tid":2497204,"uid":85127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b06e9952fd185873e44181a6b0fef8eeccd2b8bd","tid":2497204,"uid":85127,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"其實中國發生既事，關香港乜事？<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你去悼念緬甸，非洲d